<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9b59b6 0%, #8e44ad 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }

        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }

        .prescription-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #9b59b6;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: #9b59b6;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸ’Š Prescription Ready!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{patientName}},</p>

            <p>Your prescription from {{doctorName}} is now ready.</p>

            <div class="prescription-card">
                <h3>Prescription Details</h3>
                <p><strong>Prescribed by:</strong> {{doctorName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{prescriptionDate}}</p>
                <p><strong>Number of Medications:</strong> {{medicationCount}}</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>View your prescription in your medical records</li>
                <li>Order medications from our pharmacy</li>
                <li>Get them delivered to your doorstep</li>
            </ul>

            <a href="{{prescriptionUrl}}" class="button">View Prescription</a>
            <a href="{{pharmacyUrl}}" class="button" style="background: #27ae60;">Order Now</a>

            <p>Best regards,<br>The M-Clinic Kenya Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 M-Clinic Kenya. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <strong>Contact Us:</strong><br>
                Phone: 0700448448 | Email: info@mclinic.co.ke | Web: www.mclinic.co.ke
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 10px; color: #999; margin-top: 10px;">This is an automated email, please do not reply.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
